  "description": "A clear blue sky serves as the backdrop for two navy blue jet aircraft flying in formation, slightly offset from each other. The aircraft are sleek and modern, with prominent wings and a pointed nose. They appear to be performing a maneuver, with one jet slightly above and ahead of the other. The planes are the hallmark blue and gold color scheme of the Blue Angels flight demonstration squadron, with '6' visibly painted on the tail of the closer jet. The sky is uniformly bright and cloudless, providing high contrast with the dark aircraft.",
